{"tid":952122,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港速破千萬票房】《水行俠》全球收27億 積遜莫瑪亂入新人婚紗照","createTime":"2018-12-23T00:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T03:32:44.000Z","uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb34d22cb637d98f383cf8810c0d903799c5ab4","tid":952122,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:25:21.000Z","msg":"【香港速破千萬票房】《水行俠》全球收27億 積遜莫瑪亂入新人婚紗照<br />\n17小時前19.3K<br />\n即時娛樂<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVGOqXn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVGOqXn.jpg&h=482d633f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「水行俠」積遜莫瑪與家人度假<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eOpsGv4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeOpsGv4.jpg&h=7aef5f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n撞到一對新人行禮，積遜莫瑪友善答應一齊影婚紗相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fB8QEhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfB8QEhP.jpg&h=9d6b0a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n積遜莫瑪拎住三叉戟玩具入鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cBVQpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cBVQpy.jpg&h=89673d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n積遜莫瑪同現場人士合照<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q18QEh0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq18QEh0.jpg&h=49c12c7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《水行俠》全球勁收27億港元<br />\n<br />\n【新增內容】大隻型男積遜莫瑪（Jason Momoa）演出DC英雄片《水行俠》（Aquaman）於內地率先上映，之後已在全球各地陸續開畫，北美就於昨日正式開畫，周四優先場票房錄得1,370萬美元（1.07億港元），預計首個周末票房會達至8,000萬美元（6.24億港元）。《水行俠》於內地大收，今日已破15億人民幣，現時於全球票房超過3.45億美元（26.9億港元）。香港方面，周四以402萬港元成為開畫日票房冠軍，昨日已達980萬港元，今日下晝更累積至1314萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n另方面，積遜莫瑪周四與家人在夏威夷度假時，在海邊碰到一對新人正在行禮，積遜佢哋好nice咁高呼「恭喜」，仲搞鬼拎住三叉戟玩具入鏡影婚紗照。"},{"pid":"aa5f9d08f63c4a193b04438a4ddb096c714ce0e4","tid":952122,"uid":101110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:48:19.000Z","msg":"真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20191cf86ba2ab30162d595906582927ad035f3e","tid":952122,"uid":31851,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"你開緊第十一個post吹奏依套戲啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9636a003c36b4037e91ceb13187670be924878e","tid":952122,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:10:50.000Z","msg":"香港d奀星成撚日扮大牌唔同人合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad1397b918bd58a6b2c666ec4051cb2d59645b7","tid":952122,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"20191cf86ba2ab30162d595906582927ad035f3e","tid":952122,"uid":31851,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"你開緊第十一個post吹奏依套戲啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-23T01:20:45.000Z","msg":"係咩有咁多咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3894b626c4b7f21b657034e4b7d43912cf191902","tid":952122,"uid":119223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://6m6omcerdlibamtu-b2l6l7.tuziproxy.com/2cb00c6fc8beadf65185970584915b76/tumblr_pizs97byxr1uezmbko2_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F6m6omcerdlibamtu-b2l6l7.tuziproxy.com%2F2cb00c6fc8beadf65185970584915b76%2Ftumblr_pizs97byxr1uezmbko2_400.gif&h=8b9ed195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"068ec69d3af431a5fc5394f1537f7bcba6ab84ba","tid":952122,"uid":119223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T06:52:33.000Z","msg":"聖誕當做善事 幫樓主推POST加人工 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2c48d1cfe57315d58185aa4df0bed8b18b7967","tid":952122,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:11:17.000Z","msg":"帶住道具旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"